      <title>南非在与以色列发生争端后加强安全</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-01/south-africa-warns-of-israel-lawsuit-fallout-beefs-up-security</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于担心政府决定对以色列采取法律行动以试图停止与哈马斯的战争可能产生的后果，南非已加强其国家安全机构并使其处于高度戒备状态。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-01/south-africa-warns-of-israel-lawsuit-fallout-beefs-up-security</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 15:49:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国国防部长奥斯汀就癌症和住院治疗的处理方式道歉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-01/austin-apologizes-for-handling-of-cancer-and-hospitalization</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国防部长劳埃德·奥斯汀周四就他对前列腺癌手术和两周住院治疗的处理方式道歉，称他应该通知总统乔·拜登和美国公众。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-01/austin-apologizes-for-handling-of-cancer-and-hospitalization</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 15:41:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿塔尔做出新让步，法国农民将解除封锁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-01/france-s-attal-makes-new-concessions-to-tackle-farmers-concerns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国农民工会表示，在总理加布里埃尔·阿塔尔承诺采取进一步措施解决他们的担忧后，他们将暂停对该国高速公路的封锁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-01/france-s-attal-makes-new-concessions-to-tackle-farmers-concerns</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 13:39:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>有争议的南非医疗计划可能很快就会获得总统批准</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-01/south-african-president-set-to-assent-to-contentious-health-insurance-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非总统部长昆布佐·恩沙夫尼 (Khumbudzo Ntshavheni) 表示，南非总统西里尔·拉马福萨 (Cyril Ramaphosa) 可能会在今年全国大选前签署一项有争议的医疗保险法案。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-01/south-african-president-set-to-assent-to-contentious-health-insurance-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 13:37:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴拉圭寻求出售债务，投资级别接近</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-01/paraguay-sees-investment-grade-close-as-it-looks-to-raise-debt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴拉圭财政部长表示，这个拉美国家即将获得投资级地位，因为该国正在推进美元债券销售路演，并考虑用本币纸币进军全球市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-01/paraguay-sees-investment-grade-close-as-it-looks-to-raise-debt</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧尔班洞穴事件后，欧盟打破了向乌克兰提供500亿欧元援助的僵局</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-01/eu-leaders-reach-deal-to-send-ukraine-50-billion-in-aid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[匈牙利总理欧尔班维克托屈服于欧盟领导人的要求，取消了对乌克兰 500 亿欧元（540 亿美元）财政援助计划的否决，欧盟领导人达成了一项协议。福林扭转了此前因该消息而下跌的走势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-01/eu-leaders-reach-deal-to-send-ukraine-50-billion-in-aid</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 10:29:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈马斯袭击受害者家属起诉伊朗索赔10亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-01/hostage-families-demand-1-billion-over-iran-s-support-for-hamas</link>
      <description><![CDATA[10月份在以色列遭到哈马斯袭击的60多人，或者是遇难者或被劫为人质者的家属，起诉伊朗，要求其向该恐怖组织提供至少10亿美元的援助。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-01/hostage-families-demand-1-billion-over-iran-s-support-for-hamas</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 01:59:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>歌手给海莉的礼物；斯皮尔伯格、索罗斯支持拜登 2024 年参选</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-01/singer-gives-to-haley-mellon-backs-both-trump-rfk-jr-for-2024</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统候选人的数量大幅减少，但随着主要捐助者的参与，竞选资金却在增加——包括保罗·辛格、蒂莫西·梅隆和肯·格里芬——为 2024 年选举投入数百万美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-01/singer-gives-to-haley-mellon-backs-both-trump-rfk-jr-for-2024</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 01:21:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>里夫斯在劳工商业宣传中承诺冻结公司税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-01/starmer-to-vow-focus-on-growth-in-labour-pitch-to-uk-executives</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国影子财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯表示，工党政府不会提高公司利润税，因为反对党为赢得预计今年晚些时候的大选而大力支持商业。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-01/starmer-to-vow-focus-on-growth-in-labour-pitch-to-uk-executives</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 00:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥最高法院宣告政府集权改革无效</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-31/mexico-s-top-court-voids-government-s-statist-power-reform</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥最高法院在私营能源公司提起的诉讼中驳回了政府的民族主义电力立法，这对总统安德烈斯·曼努埃尔·洛佩兹·奥夫拉多尔在任期即将结束时的集权议程造成了重大打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-31/mexico-s-top-court-voids-government-s-statist-power-reform</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 23:45:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
